com.cubeia.firebase.api.lobby
Interface AttributeMapper<T>

All Known Subinterfaces:
MttAttributeMapper, TableAttributeMapper
All Known Implementing Classes:
DefaultMttAttributeMapper, DefaultTableAttributeMapper
public interface AttributeMapper<T>

This object is responsible for mapping a table to a set of attributes. It is used by the game lobby classes to transform an object into serializable attributes values.

Author:
lars.j.nilsson

Field Summary
static String MTT_NODE_TYPE_ATTRIBUTE_VALUE
          This is the string value used as a 'hint' in the system state lobby to indicate that a node in the state tree is directly representing a mtt object.
